Class JavaAPIAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • fling.adapters.JavaAPIAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PolymorphicLanguageAPIBaseAdapter

    public class JavaAPIAdapter
extends Object
implements PolymorphicLanguageAPIBaseAdapter
    Java API adapter. Output contains the API types and a single concrete implementation to be returned from the static method initiation method chains.

    Ori Roth
